subject: Basketball (College)
NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
lead_paragraph: With a victory over Michigan on Sunday, Kentucky became the first team since 1992 to reach the Final Four with five freshman starters. The last team was the Wolverines, led by the Fab Five.
